reviewText: I love this show and received these DVD's in no time.  I live in Okinawa, Japan and Amazon has always amazed me in the time they get any products I order from them - FAST!!!
I love my dvds of Old Christine. When I want to wind down I put one and and laugh anad laugh.

Hands down, this show is laugh out funny!! I own both Seasons One and Two. Iam eagerly waiting for the Third Season to come out, whenever that might be. I don't watch too many tv shows on a regular basis, but this show I definitely make it a point to watch. In fact, where I live, it's on twice the same night, one hour apart, on different channels. Sometimes I watch it both times! The combination between Julia Louis Dreyfus, and Wanda Sykes is priceless!! They work perfectly together! In fact, the whole cast does. This show has consistently great writing. I would NOT hesitate to buy every season that comes out. I know I will love it!!

Very funny when ever Im in a bad mood I can watch this show and feel better The cast is real quriky.

I loved this show when it was on - didn't miss an episode - and couldn't believe it had been cancelled. Had to the series on DVD so that I could watch it over and over again. The whole ensemble was beyond perfect and hilarious. And, by the way, I've been a fan of Julia Louise Dreyfuss before she ever appeared on Seinfield.

Not much to say and that is the best review. This is funny and you can watch over and over. Julia's acting, facial expressions, you name it are dead on. The cast is just as good. If you were one of those who never watched it when it was on network and are not sure.. buy an episode on here and see. I got the whole series after 3 episodes.

I love Julia Luis and Wanda Sykes, old Christine and her life after divorce, parenting and the
relationship she has with her brother are classic. I had to own it for myself to watch whenever I want, and need a good laugh. I will be ordering the rest of the set...... For sure!!!!

The first two seasons of Christine are very funny and you seem to care more about the characters.  All five seasons are very good but as in most shows they tend to go overboard and get zanier near the end of the series.  But overall this is a great show and first two seasons are my favorites.
The movies were shipped fast but when I got them the plastic circle in the middle that holds the DVD in place was broke. But I do enjoy them.

Everything Dreyfus touches is gold, and this is no exception. The setup is perfect and the ensemble cast is spot on. Unlike many series this one had it together from the get go, so there was no break in period during season one. Honest and silly at the same time this is classic tuff.
I always loved this series.

Very few shows make me laugh out loud, but this one does. It's hilarious!!!  There are so few shows on TV anymore that are good so I am purchasing dvd's of my favorites. This one is a must buy for me.

This show is so incredibly funny. Our DVD order came in a flash and in perfect condition. We are super happy!

Love this series.  At first, I didn't think a series about a goofy, "easy" woman would be my cup of tea.  It quickly grew on me and I found myself laughing at every member of this great cast. They work so well together and I'm only sorry the series isn't longer.  Not really for young children, but I believe adults will look forward to each episode. I think Julia Louis-Dreyfus is the best woman comedian on TV today.
